Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_nw_tim

Sets the minimum period for a new-work-request timeout. The period is specified in n-1 notation, with the increment value of 1024 clock cycles. Thus, a value of 0x0 in this register translates to 1024 cycles, 0x1 translates to 2048 cycles, 0x2 translates to 3072 cycles, etc.
